<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .container { font-family: sans-serif; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
        .otp { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50; letter-spacing: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2> <p>Please use the following code to verify your email address:</p>
        <p class="otp"><%= otp %></p> <p>This code is valid for <strong>2 minutes</strong>.</p>
        <p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>